55 turgidāḥ bhavanty, atha paścāt punar navīkṛtā
56 sva-varṇena ekaikā, pūrvam yat sūryaḥ
57 nayati sva-aśvān anya-nakṣatrasya adhaḥ;

64 Yadi aham varṇayitum śaknuvām katham aham nidrāṃ prāpaḥ
65 Siringāyāḥ nirmāyāḥ śrutvā,
66 tāsām nayanaṃ yasmāt jāgaraṇaṃ tathāpi ati-maṅgalyam āsid;

67 yathā citrakāraḥ yaḥ ādarśena citram ālikhati,
68 aham ālikhayema katham aham nidrāṃ prāpaḥ;
69 kim tu yaḥ ko'pi yaḥ nidrāṃ śubham eva kalpayitum icchati.

79 dṛṣṭavānś ca svīyam gaṇam hīnam
80 tathā Mauṣeḥ tathā Īlīyāyāḥ,
81 guror api vastram parivṛttam;

100 Iha tvam alpam kālam āraṇyavāsaḥ bhaviṣyasi;
101 mama saha anantam kālam sādhāraṇa-nagara-vāsaḥ bhaviṣyasi
102 tasyāḥ Romāyāḥ yatra Khristos Rāmaṇīyaḥ asti.

112 yathā aham adṛkṣam avataraṇam pakṣiṇaḥ divyasya
113 vṛkṣasya adhaḥ, bhindantam tvacaḥ,
114 kim uta puṣpāṇi api nava-pallavāni ca;

115 tataś ca tasya ratham āhataḥ sarveṇa balena;
116 yataḥ sa vyavartata yathā nāvaḥ samudre,
117 abhibhūtā tarangeṇa, kadācit dakṣiṇataḥ, kadācit vāmatataḥ.

118 Tataḥ paśyāmi ekām śṛgālīm ākramaṇakāriṇīm
119 jaya-ratha-śayyāyām,
120 yā sarvasyānna-pānasya upavāsita iva ābhāti sma;

130 Tataḥ me pratyabhāsata yathā pṛthivī vivṛtā syāt
131 ubhayor cakrayoḥ madhye, tataś ca apaśyam niḥsṛtaṃ sarpaṃ
132 yaḥ ratham prati puccham sthāpayām āsa;

148 Surakṣitā, yathā durgam ucche parvate,
149 āsīna āsīt uttareṇa ekaṃ veśyāṃ muktāṃ,
150 mayā dṛṣṭā sārdham bhrukuṭīṃ kṛtvā;

151 tasyāḥ apaharaṇam mā bhavet iti yathā,
152 paśyāmi tasyāḥ pakṣe ekam dānavam;
153 kadācit te ubhau parस्param चुम्बितवन्तौ.

154 Api tu yasmāt me cupidaṃ ca viṣaya-viṣayaṃ ca cakṣuḥ
155 Abhyavartata, sa ugraḥ kāma-patiḥ
156 Tām śīrṣṇo mūrdhānaṃ prāpya pādayor antam tāḍayām āsa;
